lass=\"reply-list-item--detail\">把广告牌识别成车修复了吗？</div>\n                     </div>\n                  </li>\n               </ul>\n               <div class=\"back-comment-item--detail\">把广告牌识别成车修复了吗？</div>\n\n               <div class=\"back-comment-item--operation\">\n                  <div class=\"back-comment-item--time\">昨天&nbsp;01:45</div>\n                  <div class=\"back-comment-item--place\">黑龙江</div>\n                  <a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"back-comment-item--reply back-comment-item--closeReply\" data-comment-id=\"249286987\">关闭回复</a>\n               </div>\n\n               <div class=\"back-comment-item--replyBox\" >\n                  <div class=\"back-comment-publish\">\n                     <textarea class=\"back-comment-publish--textarea\" @focus=\"focusFunc\" @blur=\"blurFunc\" placeholder=\"我来说两句…\"></textarea>\n                     <span class=\"back-comment-publish--num\">0/100</span>\n                     <a class=\"back-comment-publish--button\" href=\"#\">发表评论</a>\n                  </div>\n               </div>\n\n            </div>\n          </section>\n        </section>\n      </section>\n      <div class=\"back-comment-box--more\">\n        <span class=\"text\">查看更多&nbsp;374&nbsp;条评论</span>\n        <span class=\"icon\"></span>\n      </div>\n    </section>    </div>\n          <section class=\"info-recommend\" id=\"recommendApp\">\n\n          </section> </section> <section class=\"content-right\" id=\"asideContent\">\n </section></section> <section class=\"right-comment-layer\" id=\"rightCommentApp\">\n     <section class=\"right-comment\">\n       <h3 class=\"right-comment-head\">\n         <div class=\"right-comment-head--title\">评论(374)</div>\n         <div class=\"right-comment-head--rule\">\n            请遵守<a href=\"#\" class=\"right-comment-head--ruleLink\">《搜狐我来说两句用户公约》</a>\n         </div>\n         <a href=\"#\" class=\"right-comment--close\" @click=\"closeLayer\"></a>\n       </h3>\n       <div class=\"right-comm